{"tid":2339770,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"肯德基推出遊戲主機KFConsole　內建「暖雞室」玩遊戲同時保溫炸雞","createTime":"2020-12-25T02:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T18:15:04.000Z","uid":185631,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"03f1b8f363357d6aadff4f923008e1f7ef696b82","tid":2339770,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:22:07.000Z","msg":"肯德基（KFC）在今年6月SONY宣布PlayStation 5登場後翌日，宣布將推出遊戲主機，惟當時外界一直以為僅是營銷手法。KFC旗下遊戲部門「KFC Gaming」於美國時間22日正式宣布，新主機「KFConsole」即將登場，而KFConsole更會採用Intel NUC規格。<br />\n<br />\nKFC Gaming在Twitter上表示，其遊戲主機KFConsole將正式登場。主機結合Intel NUC 套件、華碩GeForce RTX顯卡、Seagate PCIe NVMe SSD和Cooler Master 客製機殼。而且支援VR模式，畫面支援更達4K 240Hz級別。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，該主機採用受「肯德基烤雞桶」所啟發的圓筒狀造型設計，內建創新的「暖雞室」，讓用家玩遊戲同時也可利用氣炸鍋烤雞及保溫。<br />\n<br />\n雖然目前官方仍未公布KFConsole詳細規格資訊以及具體上市計畫，不過仍可肯定此企劃並非虛擬的宣傳手法，而是真有其事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2835000/2836080/KFC_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2835000%2F2836080%2FKFC_1024.png&h=9b868a4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G2xa7vabDkE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DG2xa7vabDkE&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt5B82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=ee62aa8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G2xa7vabDkE</a>"},{"pid":"07368361ddfe63a347d11a6fb09cba8a8588cd6a","tid":2339770,"uid":301523,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:25:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 部機油淋淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac63f007ba6e709adad6f5ad16bb378fdc4c8832","tid":2339770,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T02:26:49.000Z","msg":"有實機咪信囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi